headline: Coinbase Posts Mixed Earnings Results That Missed Forecasts. The Stock Is Down.
summary: Crypto investment firm  Coinbase Global  reported mixed results for the first quarter Thursday.  Analysts tracked by FactSet were expecting revenue of $2.1 billion and earnings per share of $1.93.  Shares of  Coinbase  fell 3% in after-hours trading.

headline: Coinbase Stock Has Tumbled. What to Watch for in Earnings.
summary: Bitcoin  has been on a wild ride this year, just like the stock market.  Will that be good news for crypto asset manager and brokerage firm  Coinbase Global  as it gets set to report earnings Thursday afternoon?  Coinbase  has also been whipsawed by the volatility in stocks and cryptocurrencies.
